---
layout: base
title: Welcome to Paradise - Uvita & Ojochal, Costa Rica
description: Discover the natural beauty and vibrant lifestyle of Uvita and Ojochal, Costa Rica. Your guide to beaches, wildlife, and sustainable living in Costa Rica's southern Pacific coast.
---

<section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
        <h1>Discover Paradise in Uvita & Ojochal</h1>
        <p>Where the rainforest meets the Pacific, and adventure awaits around every corner</p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Welcome to Costa Rica's Hidden Gem</h2>
        <div class="grid">
            {% for card in featuredCards.cards %}
            <div class="card hover-lift">
                {% if card.image %}
                <img src="{{ card.image }}" alt="{{ card.title }}" loading="lazy">
                {% endif %}
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h3>{{ card.title }}</h3>
                    <p>{{ card.description }}</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

{% if collections.posts %}
<section class="section alternate">
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Latest Stories</h2>
        <div class="grid">
            {% for post in collections.posts | reverse | limit(3) %}
            <div class="card">
                {% if post.data.image %}
                <img src="{{ post.data.image }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }}" loading="lazy">
                {% endif %}
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
                    <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
                    <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="button">Read More</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
{% endif %}
